 <para>If the <emphasis>Worksheet</emphasis> button visible, it may be used to access to the table which contains the columns for the selected curve.</para>

<sect2 id="custom-curves-dialog-lines">
<title>Custom curves for lines and scatter plots</title>

  <para>The first tab on the right side of the dialog window allows definition of the pair of axes to which a curve is attached. Attaching different curves on the layer to different X/Y axis pairs permits placing several curves with different x/y scales on the same plot layer.</para>
  <figure id="fig-custom-curves-line-1">
