    </mediaobject>
  </figure>

 <para>The second tab on the right side of the dialog window allows customizing the style of the plot line (color, line style, thickness). The connect button allows changing the style which is used to draw the selected curve (steps, droplines, etc). See the &plot-menu-lnk; to see the different types of plots available.</para>
  <figure id="fig-custom-curves-line-1">
