  <para>The fields on the right are used to define the fill style used for pie segments. The <emphasis>First color </emphasis>combo-box defines which color is used for the first segment. The remaining segments will be filled with colors that follow the order defined in the combo-box's list. The default value for this field is black, so segments 2, 3, ... will be red, green, etc.</para>
